12- Chart Object - Map 12

The map is an essential piece of our dashboard

One of the business requirements was to see the location where we had any conversions

For this we used two field in our map layer:

  • Location
  • Conversions (ClassSignupID)


Below is a picture of our finish product


The following steps are used to make this map

  • First we drag and drop a map from ‘Assets’ and onto our sheet
  • Next we search for our Conversions and Location fields respectively, and them onto the map as point layer.


Next we need to format the map in other to blend it out dashboard.

For this we need to:

  • Reduce the size of the points, in the ‘layer settings’
  • Change the color, in the ‘Map settings’
  • Remove the legend, in the ‘Appearance’
